7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F27%2F114136_20d860a4ad7eeb3a978fe80fdf4162f7.jpg&h=b2af6d0a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n會員 米已成炊 狙擊趕至, <strong>我唔係屈機男</strong> 發起第2次鬥捐錢活動, 並再次以<strong>敗者永久退出連登</strong>為賭注<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/216195/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/216195/page/1</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/27/114554_d63c6683aa8e5ec7011afc9beb8e082e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F27%2F114554_d63c6683aa8e5ec7011afc9beb8e082e.jpg&h=56996aed&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n今次結果更加柒, 自己開盤自己潛水, 會員 米已成炊 不戰而勝<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/217870/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/217870/page/1</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/27/114851_dd793b0a7bdc7b6717320a1b5602eb1a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F27%2F114851_dd793b0a7bdc7b6717320a1b5602eb1a.jpg&h=0c512bab&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n今日走數狗 <strong>我唔係屈機男 #40470</strong> 言而無信又再一次上水..."},{"pid":"7250a6fc4a212c47068872c4a87a57ed597c1e42","tid":374844,"uid":94399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T04:00:08.000Z","msg":"關你撚事咩"},{"pid":"853112441b8863ea22547b45d0d142d149f114d4","tid":374844,"uid":26003,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T04:04:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>關你撚事咩</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"341f15e1aa43b778d34014abc653d1da0a72f282","tid":374844,"uid":80814,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T05:43:45.000Z","msg":"Ocamp好應該收皮<br />\n根本係畀機會獸父獸母<br />\n揀女揀仔來淫亂派對<br />\n某U嘅大O直頭係畀班左膠揀卒<br />\n做社運乞衣繼承人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n本身係摺友玩ocamp